[30;1m648 | [0m[35m   previous used ``distutils.version`` to examine version numbers of dependencies[0m
[30;1m649 | [0m[35m   at run time, and now use ``packaging.version`` for this. This is a new[0m
[30;1m650 | [0m[35m   dependency.[0m
[30;1m651 | [0m[35m-  Fixed an error message advising the user that Ghostscript was not installed being[0m
[30;1m652 | [0m[35m   suppressed when this condition actually happens.[0m

[30;1m63 | [0m[35mto make page rotation more (less) aggressive. The threshold number is the ratio[0m
[30;1m64 | [0m[35mof how confidence the OCR engine is that the document image should be changed,[0m
[30;1m65 | [0m[35mcompared to kept the same. The default value is quite conservative; on some files[0m
[30;1m66 | [0m[35mit may not attempt rotations at all unless it is very confident that the current[0m
[30;1m67 | [0m[35mrotation is wrong. A lower value of ``2.0`` will produce more rotations, and[0m
[30;1m68 | [0m[35mmore false positives. Run with ``-v1`` to see the confidence level for each[0m
[30;1m69 | [0m[35mpage to see if there may be a better value for your files.[0m

[30;1m280 | [0m[35m[0m

   Pattern: [32m\s(advpack\.dll|appvlp|at|atbroker|bash|bginfo|bitsadmin|cdb|certutil|cl_invocation\.ps1|cl_mutexverifiers\.ps1|cmd|cmdkey|cmstp|comsvcs\.dll|control|csc|cscript|csi|devtoolslauncher|dfsvc|diskshadow|dnscmd|dnx|dotnet|dxcap|esentutl|eventvwr|excel|expand|extexport|extrac32|findstr|forfiles|ftp|gfxdownloadwrapper|gpscript|hh|ie4uinit|ieadvpack\.dll|ieaframe\.dll|ic|infdefaultinstall|installutil|jsc|makecab|manage-bde\.wsf|mavinject|mftrace|microsoft\.workflow\.compiler|mmc|msbuild|msconfig|msdeploy|msdt|mshta|mshtml\.dll|msc|msxsl|netsh|odbcconf|pcalua|pcwrun|pcwutl\.dll|pester\.bat|powerpnt|presentationhost|pubprn\.vbs|rcsi|reg|regasm|regedit|register-cimprovider|regsvcs|regsvr32|rpcping|rundll32|runonce|runscripthelper|sc|schtasks|scriptrunner|setupapi\.dll|shdocvw\.dll|shell32\.dll|slmgr\.vbs|sqldumper|sqlps|sqltoolsps|squirrel|syncappvpublishingserver|syncappvpublishingserver\.vbs|syssetup\.dll|te|tracker|tttracer|update|url\.dll|verclsid|vsjitdebugger|wab|winrm\.vbs|winword|wmic|wscript|wsl|wsreset|xwizard|zipfldr\.dll)\s[0m
[30;1m25 | [0m[35mOCRmyPDF uses a custom concurrent executor which can support either threads or[0m
[30;1m26 | [0m[35mprocesses with the same interface. This is useful because OCRmyPDF can use[0m
[30;1m27 | [0m[35meither threads or processes to parallelize work, whichever is more appropriate[0m
[30;1m28 | [0m[35mfor the task at hand.[0m
[30;1m29 | [0m[35m[0m
[30;1m30 | [0m[35mThe interface is currently private and subject to change. In particular, if[0m
[30;1m31 | [0m[35mexperiments with asyncio and anyio are successful, the interface will change.[0m
